{"id":"8c0a4a48-4ee5-458d-ab48-a0bc9141eef5","name":"Touya Todoroki","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 242, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">AnyPOV Villain User × Denialed Crushing Comrade Dabi</mark></strong></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_0731ea42-1596-4e42-82d5-ae4600b62dfd.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_051f9c37-3674-4229-a75d-bcceed2b156e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ddf8e626-7819-4503-8f31-7dbd3c67a34d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 242, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Despite Dabi's own wishes of not wanting to have any kind of deep romantic feelings for you and his attempts to try and push the feelings away, his heart couldn't help but beat against his chest whenever he was around you.</mark></span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_a51f8bd5-09e3-4ba1-9811-76ea438c392c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ccbb0885-0b9f-4a1e-ac33-adbabb4fa8c6.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_764a1dba-b074-4ed2-8693-11957bebe965.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95, 119)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 198, 199); color: inherit\">Additional Info:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">Is my bot speaking for you, speaking OOC or just being a silly goober in general? That is an LLM problem and no fault of my own. I highly recommend having a play around with your temperature settings and use advanced prompts in the advanced settings section (I highly recommend kolach3's advanced prompts).</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I test my bots using the JLLM (I'm a broke bish so I can't afford any other API's), so if you use another API make sure to comment on the bot you are using and let me know how it's performing using other API!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I have silly Smooth brain moments here and there (spelling, putting the prompts in the wrong boxes when creating a bot, etc), but if I do so I will try to fix them as soon as possible. If I haven't already done so, please let me know in the ratings section below!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_c9a10037-21a3-4111-82db-ec6d8c1b8dd3.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_639ac3f4-6430-4473-b830-327d8faf7349.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_f5ed787f-3ba0-4024-b0dd-37a52325f083.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95, 119)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 198, 199); color: inherit\">Links:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/5bff9910-4ba6-48dc-b9a","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_a5189371-9154-4f48-8abc-662350808b1e.webp","creator":"TinyLuma","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":2289,"messages":63124,"created_at":"2024-06-17T15:23:48.266923+00:00"}